	(11284,73,'page_header','Who We Are'),
	(11285,73,'page_sub_header','BrainDo is a full-service, interactive agency with one goal: <strong>Help Our Clients Succeed Online.</strong>'),
	(11286,73,'first_paragraph','BrainDo is a collection of hard working go-getters and experts that come together to create great things for our clients. Our experience lets us cut through the fads and develop the strategy and tactics that truly work to build brand experience and bring measurable results.'),
	(11287,73,'paragraph_header_1','We Get It.'),
	(11288,73,'paragraph_text_1','Our brains aren’t wired faster, we just care more about getting it right. Our team understands how to grow, sustain and reimagine digital brands. We draw on our combined expertise of 50+ years in Digital Marketing having touched on nearly every vertical including: Travel, Automotive, Insurance, Legal, Pharmaceutical, Ecommerce, B2B, Health/Beauty & Fitness and Entertainment.'),
	(11289,73,'paragraph_header_2','We Get It Done.'),
	(11290,73,'paragraph_text_2','The number one reason our clients like us, put simply, “We Get it Done.” Great strategy doesn’t mean squat if you can’t execute – and we execute with precision. We believe clients have the right to great results in a timely fashion and we continue to be the agency known for getting it done and doing it well.'),
	(11291,73,'employee_block_header','Meet the Team'),
	(11292,73,'employee_name','Ben Stuart'),
	(11293,73,'employee_title','Web Analytics & Tag Management'),
	(11294,73,'employee_description','Ben is a die-hard tech enthusiast, building computers in his spare time and then using those computers to develop smart analytics solutions and implement management plans (including detailed documentation flow charts) for our clients.'),
	(11295,73,'employee_image_url','benstuart.jpg'),
	(11296,73,'employee_hover_image_url','benstuart-hover.jpg'),
	(11297,73,'employee_selected_image_url','benstuart-selected.jpg'),
	(11298,73,'employee_name','Bill Paffas'),
	(11299,73,'employee_title','CRO & User Experience'),
	(11300,73,'employee_description','As resident CRO expert, Bill combines his years of digital analytics experience with a keen understanding of user experience. When not testing websites, he often performs multivariate tests on his two dogs: Ralph & Rufus.'),
