ogo that played with shape and lines and worked well with the right typeface. It’s modern, energetic and subtly suggests the notion of moving forward. It feels like a logo that can stand the test of time, and that’s what we’re counting on.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-311 border\" src=\"http://dev.brain.do/wp-content/themes/BrainDo/library/images/blog/reimagining-braindo-logo-4.jpg\" alt=\"reimagining-braindo-logo-4\" width=\"4167\" height=\"1625\" />','Reimagining the BrainDo Brand Logo','','inherit','open','open','','294-revision-v1','','','2014-11-17 10:51:01','2014-11-17 15:51:01','',294,'http://dev.brain.do/294-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
